World class compound with stunning panoramic views set in the exclusive guard gated Bella Vista Estates on 7.5 acres. Behind personal gates providing ample security and privacy, the ~13,000 square foot home incapsulates dramatic architecture infused with elegance and sophistication. State of the art accommodations throughout with 8 bedrooms, 11 bathrooms, multiple quintessential living spaces, a chef's kitchen, bar, custom movie theatre, game room, and wine cellar. Exuding luxury, the impressive master suite encompasses a sitting room, fireplace, walk- in closets, spacious stone filled bathrooms and a private balcony boasting unobstructed views. Hosting one of the most impressive outdoor settings in all of Los Angeles, the private backyard showcases an infinity edge pool, spa, cold plunge, outdoor kitchen with a pizza oven, dining, and large lawn area. Ample parking with a 4-car garage, motor court, driveway and additional space across the street adjacent to the private sport court and playground. The pinnacle of Beverly Hills.

Floor to ceiling glass doors from each room vanish offering LA's finest indoor/outdoor flow. The expansive master suite with a sitting room, fireplace, custom dual walk-in closets, and a stone-filled luxurious bathroom boasts city views through the wall of glass that slides open to the backyard. Sensational and sleek backyard with a state-of-the-art kitchen, raised edge infinity pool, spa, fire feature, dining area and lounge space. Designed to elevate the art of living and entertaining, the home is fully operated and secured by smart systems.

NEW LISTING! 960 N Alpine Dr • Beverly Hills • $38,000,000 🏆🏆🏆

A true trophy of mid-century modern design showcasing luxury, unparalleled scale, and sophistication. Upon arrival, large double gates open revealing the private driveway lined with abundant greenery oﬀering ample privacy and security. Beyond the front door, the custom home features several unrivaled living spaces, 4 bedrooms and 7 bathrooms. An exquisite infusion of rich hues and textures with solid teak-paneled ceilings running above the concrete ﬂoors. Marble countertops and backsplash in the chef's kitchen draw a beautiful contrast to the teak island and surrounding custom walnut cabinets. From the great room, living room, and master bedroom, glass doors slide open putting the stunning city views on display. The unmatched grounds, by esteemed landscape architect Mark Rios, showcase a stunning pool, large grass area, and a covered patio. With a state-of-the-art security system and the latest technology, the home is secured and operated by a Control4 system personalized to your lifestyle providing unparalleled convenience. Enjoy a lifestyle of seclusion, luxurious comfort & lavish entertaining.

node.text:
JUST LISTED! 601 Via Del Monte • Palos Verdes Estates • $7,995,000 🔥🔥💪

Showcasing breathtaking panoramic ocean views, this quintessential estate is set above the coastline in the heart of Malaga Cove. Offering unparalleled luxury, exquisite finishes, soaring ceilings, and advanced technology, the home boasts ~6,000 square feet with 5 bedrooms, 7 bathrooms and an elevator with custom stonework servicing all 3 levels. The masterfully designed open floor plan features several incredible living/entertaining spaces all with views, a chef's kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances, informal dining, a bonus room with an additional kitchen, and movie theatre. Walls of glass vanish throughout both levels allowing for a seamless flow from the inside of the home to the outside. California living at its finest. The stunning master suite is second to none with wood beam ceilings, an expansive private balcony, a spa-like bathroom with a free-standing tub, and 2 walk-in closets. Unmatched outdoor living hosting an expansive pool, spa, several patios + balconies, a fire pit, built-in BBQ, a dining area, ample lounge space, and a large grass area.

node.text:
JUST LISTED! 25211 Jim Bridger Rd • Hidden Hills • $13,995,000 💥💥💥

World class Hidden Hills Estate with captivating canyon views and dramatic architecture spanning 13,211 square feet of pure elegance and sophistication. Enter into the beautiful 2 story foyer showcasing soaring ceilings, Chevron flooring and a floating staircase. Beyond the entry, the great room seamlessly flows into the striking kitchen outfitted in custom cabinetry, 2 stone topped islands and top of the line appliances. Travel upstairs to the luxurious master suite complete with a large balcony overlooking the stunning grounds, dual baths, and dual closets. Unmatched amenities throughout including an additional 6 ensuite bedrooms, a large media room, office, gym, glass encased temperature-controlled wine display, bar and state of the art security system. Hosting an unmatched outdoor setting perfect for both entertaining and intimate settings, the backyard features an infinity edge pool that drops off to unobstructed canyon views, a spa, covered barbeque area, and a spacious grass area. Providing the utmost privacy and seclusion, the estate is located in the Ashley Ridge section of Hidden Hills. Ample parking with a 4-car garage and large circular driveway lined by manicured landscape.
